WEBVTT

00:00:30.229 --> 00:00:31.719
Svako jutro budi me ovaj zvuk,

00:00:31.719 --> 00:00:33.685
kao da sam princeza
iz Disneyjevog crtića.

00:00:33.685 --> 00:00:34.718
(Smijeh)

00:00:35.164 --> 00:00:36.370
Ja sam poduzetnik

00:00:36.394 --> 00:00:40.774
i živim od toga da pomažem
drugima da zasade takve šume.

00:00:40.798 --> 00:00:42.722
Dosad smo pomagali tvornicama,

00:00:42.746 --> 00:00:43.903
farmama,

00:00:43.927 --> 00:00:45.085
školama,

00:00:46.287 --> 00:00:47.442
kućanstvima,

00:00:48.306 --> 00:00:49.482
odmaralištima,

00:00:50.273 --> 00:00:51.629
stambenim naseljima,

00:00:52.891 --> 00:00:54.131
javnim parkovima,

00:00:54.854 --> 00:00:56.197
pa i zoološkom vrtu

00:00:56.221 --> 00:00:57.730
da zasade jednu takvu šumu.

00:00:58.715 --> 00:01:03.009
Šuma nije nužno izolirani komad zemlje
gdje zajedno žive životinje.